 the House with some sort of a plan. October 12, 2019 In "Entertainment" Mercy Eke, was the cynosure of Big Brother Naija season four grand finale on Sunday, as she was crowned the winner of the show. October 7, 2019 In "Entertainment" Mercy Eke By Sylvester Kwentua Big Brother Naija 2019 winner and media darling, Mercy Eke may have just started living the life of a celebrity, but has come out on social media, to say she needs her old life back, because according to her, living the life of a celebrity… November 27, 2019 In "Entertainment"